2.0.0-alpha.readme:
# web3-eth-iban

This is a sub module of [web3.js][repo]

This is the IBAN module to be used in the `web3-eth` module.
Please read the [documentation][docs] for more.

## Installation

```bash
npm install web3-eth-iban
```

## Usage

```js
import {Iban} from 'web3-eth-iban';

new Iban('XE75JRZCTTLBSYEQBGAS7GID8DKR7QY0QA3');
```

## Types 

All the typescript typings are placed in the types folder. 

[docs]: http://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/1.0/
[repo]: https://github.com/ethereum/web3.js

2.0.0-alpha.1.name: web3-eth-iban
2.0.0-alpha.1.description: This package converts Ethereum addresses to IBAN addresses a vice versa.
2.0.0-alpha.1.readme:
# web3-eth-iban

This is a sub module of [web3.js][repo]

This is the IBAN module to be used in the `web3-eth` module.
Please read the [documentation][docs] for more.

## Installation

```bash
npm install web3-eth-iban
```

## Usage

```js
import {Iban} from 'web3-eth-iban';

new Iban('XE75JRZCTTLBSYEQBGAS7GID8DKR7QY0QA3');
```

## Types 

All the typescript typings are placed in the types folder. 

[docs]: http://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/1.0/
[repo]: https://github.com/ethereum/web3.js
